<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt einige Bürger und Kaufleute zu Köln an und bittet um Unterstützung für ihre Forderungen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_489" id="244r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l1"><expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als etlıch <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd kawflewte <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Cölen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l4">etwas 
<del rend="strikethrough">beÿ </del> ſache vnd rechnung beÿ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_489_line_1576399651032_637">ew </ab></add> cʒe handeln <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l5">weiſheit von Jn <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wirdt / . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſie vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l6"><expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vmb einen <expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> petbrief an ew / Vnd alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l7"><expan>bıt<ex>en</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> von Jren <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ſie ew bevolhen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l8">ſein laſſen vnd Jn <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſein wöllet / . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_489" id="244r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als etlich
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kawflewte <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Cölen etwas sache und rechnung bey <add>ew</add> cze handeln
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als ewr weisheit von in
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
                        wirdt, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie uns <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        umb einen <expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> petbrief an ew; und also
                                <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> von iren <expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan>
                        daz ir sie ew bevolhen sein lassen und in <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        sein wöllet. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
